{"tid":1240400,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"AV女優一花琴音自爆患子宮頸癌","createTime":"2019-06-18T10:29:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-18T10:49:16.000Z","uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"022cb5a347271d81b8485691a87701b01fc36d35","tid":1240400,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:29:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190618/photo/bkn-20190618172154529-0618_00862_001_01b.jpg?20190618174451\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190618%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190618172154529-0618_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20190618174451&h=4b3715c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本AV女優一花琴音，今日在Twitter透露不幸患上子宮頸癌。她表示癌細胞有機會擴散，預定7月入院接受手術，並會跟醫生商量，如期參與已接下的工作及活動。去年10月，AV界驚爆愛滋風波時，她曾力証自己沒有受感染，其後更宣布引退，今年3月由「寶生莉莉」改名「一花琴音」復出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190618/photo/bkn-20190618172154529-0618_00862_001_02b.jpg?20190618174451\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190618%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190618172154529-0618_00862_001_02b.jpg%3F20190618174451&h=1329bce1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前AV女優麻美由真，2013年亦曾驚爆患子宮頸癌，並要切除子宫及卵巢保命，但近年她的健康情况好轉不少，抗癌成功後從良做歌手。"},{"pid":"0913c67c399a1ef34396255aba202a2442b07bbd","tid":1240400,"uid":93958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T10:49:16.000Z","msg":"hpv<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}